# ğŸ”¥ Quick Comparison

| Feature         | List  | Dictionary   |
| --------------- | ----- | ------------ |
| Ordered         | âœ… Yes | âœ… Yes (3.7+) |
| Mutable         | âœ… Yes | âœ… Yes        |
| Index-based     | âœ… Yes | âŒ No         |
| Key-value pairs | âŒ No  | âœ… Yes        |

---

# ğŸš€ Simple Summary

* **List** â†’ Stores multiple values in order.
* **List Comprehension** â†’ Short way to create lists.
* **Dictionary** â†’ Stores data as keyâ€“value pairs.

